30:59.383 --> 31:03.057
<i>Oh, I still believe ♪</i>

31:10.973 --> 31:13.011
<i>Pick it up ♪</i>

31:13.044 --> 31:15.048
<i>As we go along ♪</i>

31:20.125 --> 31:22.531
<i>I still believe ♪</i>

31:22.564 --> 31:24.701
<i>Through the shame ♪</i>

31:24.734 --> 31:27.173
<i>And through the grief ♪</i>

31:27.206 --> 31:29.645
<i>Through the heartache ♪</i>

31:29.678 --> 31:32.049
<i>Through the tears ♪</i>

31:32.082 --> 31:34.253
<i>Through the waiting ♪</i>

31:34.286 --> 31:36.525
<i>Through the years ♪</i>

31:36.558 --> 31:38.696
<i>For people like us ♪</i>

31:38.729 --> 31:41.401
<i>In places like this ♪</i>

31:41.434 --> 31:43.673
<i>We need all the hope ♪</i>

31:43.706 --> 31:45.677
